Agriterra professionalises ambitious farmer cooperatives and organisations worldwide.
  
Agriterra believes in farmer ownership to fight poverty and stimulates social-economic strong and vibrant rural areas. Cooperative expertise and peer-to-peer advice from the Dutch agri & food top sector are key principles; advice, training and exchange the key methodologies.
  
Agriterra developed a range of practical training products for cooperatives and agricultural organisations in developing countries.
  
Under this project, trainings on business development are covered. Agriterra developed several products and trainings on this topic:
  
•       Training of trainers My.COOP
  
•       Marketing basics training
  
•       Financial sustainable services
  
•       Value Creator

Professional farmer cooperatives and organisations, bankable cooperatives who are resulting in profitability, solvency and higher incomes for members.

The cooperative would like to  professionalize in the activity of collecting and selling rice of its members  in order to make it more profitable. So  they can earn more income and sell large quantities of quality rice to the Bralima.
all scopings visits cooperative and organisation assessments and audit services related to Agriterra supported projects can be registered under this project for 2019

L'activité fondamental de la CECAFEP consiste a collecter l'épargne des paysans et leur octroyer des crédits en cas de besoin.La politique de crédit mis en vigeur ainsi que les textes de base qui régissent cette coopec sont encore limité pour que tous les membres puissent participer équitablement aux activités réalisées .Certaines clauses des statuts ne prennent pas  compte  de la dynamique  genre qui est entrain d'etre réalisé dans les pratiques faites. La composition des organes constitue un des aspects qui seront analysé en vue d'assurer la participation de toutes les catégories  de membres.
Improve coop's strategic management and enhance their marketing so they can better position them in the competitive market.

L'objectif fondamental pour la cecafep consiste a réaliser le recadrage de sa politique de crédit en vue d'accroitre la participation de tous les membres surtout les jeunes aux activités d'épargne et de crédit.

1. Organize the coop to participate a strategic planning workshop by Agriterra in March
  2. Conduct an advisory service on marketing in Q2
  3. Provide emplyee/BA service on product development and branding for the coop
  4. Provide employee/BA service on market linkage introducing coop's produts to certain platforms and buyers
  5. Organize a study tour involving the coop; this is subject to funding availability
